  "createbigcannons.ponder.cannon_mount/upside_down_cannon_mounts.header": "火炮底座的倒置放置",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.cannon_mount/upside_down_cannon_mounts.text_1": "使用扳手右击火炮底座的侧面可将其旋转朝下。",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.cannon_mount/upside_down_cannon_mounts.text_2": "火炮底座也可以倒置放置在方块底部。",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.cannon_mount/using_extensions.header": "火炮底座拓展件的使用",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.cannon_mount/using_extensions.text_1": "火炮底座拓展件为方块提供了额外的接口区域。",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.cannon_mount/using_extensions.text_2": "它们会沿侧面箭头方向延伸所指向的火炮底座。",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.cannon_mount/using_fixed_cannon_mounts.header": "固定火炮底座的使用",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.cannon_mount/using_fixed_cannon_mounts.text_1": "固定火炮底座可用于将火炮瞄准同一位置。",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.cannon_mount/using_fixed_cannon_mounts.text_2": "它们不接收动力输入，必须通过侧面接口手动设置。",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.cannon_mount/using_fixed_cannon_mounts.text_3": "与固定火炮底座的交互与普通火炮底座类似，使用相同的控制面。",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.cannon_mount/using_fixed_cannon_mounts.text_4": "火炮装配",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.cannon_mount/using_fixed_cannon_mounts.text_5": "开火",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.cannon_mount/using_fixed_cannon_mounts.text_6": "固定火炮底座无法被拓展。",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.cannon_mount/using_fixed_cannon_mounts.text_7": "使用扳手旋转固定火炮底座。",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.munitions/wet_ammo_storage.header": "用水浸泡保护弹药及其副作用",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.munitions/wet_ammo_storage.text_1": "推进剂块和抛射物均易受火焰和其他爆炸的影响而爆炸。",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.munitions/wet_ammo_storage.text_2": "弹药块可以通过浸水来防止火焰和爆炸。",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.munitions/wet_ammo_storage.text_3": "然而，浸水会使推进剂块变得潮湿。",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.munitions/wet_ammo_storage.text_4": "潮湿的推进剂效果更弱，且如果作为火炮的第一块推进剂则无法点燃。",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.munitions/wet_ammo_storage.text_5": "解决办法是让潮湿的推进剂自然晾干，无法像湿海绵那样在熔炉中烘干。",
  "createbigcannons.ponder.munitions/wet_ammo_storage.text_6": "然而，放置在下界等炎热环境中的推进剂会像湿海绵一样瞬间变干。",
